        require(balance1After <= balance1Before + amount1Out, "Pancake: SUSPICIOUS_BALANCE_INCREASE_1");

        uint amount0In = balance0After > _reserve0 - amount0Out ? balance0After - (_reserve0 - amount0Out) : 0;
        uint amount1In = balance1After > _reserve1 - amount1Out ? balance1After - (_reserve1 - amount1Out) : 0;

        // 添加价格影响限制（例如，单笔交易输入不得超过储备的5%）
        require(amount0In <= _reserve0 / 20, "Pancake: PRICE_IMPACT_TOO_HIGH");
        require(amount1In <= _reserve1 / 20, "Pancake: PRICE_IMPACT_TOO_HIGH");
        // ... 后续K值检查 ...
    }
    ```

#### 4.2 补丁验证结果
- **验证方式**：在模拟环境中，对PancakeSwap Pair合约应用上述**价格影响限制补丁**（即4.1中的第2点），随后重放原始攻击交易(`0x77cf448ceaf8f66e06d1537ef83218725670d3a509583ea0d161533fda56c063`)。
