## 4. 修复与验证 (Mitigation & Verification)

### 核心修复策略

#### 修复一：加强代理合约权限检查
**修复目标**：防止逻辑合约管理员绕过代理安全机制

**核心补丁代码**：
```solidity
function _beforeFallback() internal virtual override {
    // 不仅检查代理管理员，还要检查逻辑合约的关键权限
    address logicAdmin = ILogicContract(_implementation()).getAdmin();
    require(msg.sender != _getAdmin() && msg.sender != logicAdmin, 
            "TransparentUpgradeableProxy: admin or logic admin cannot fallback to proxy target");

    // 添加白名单机制：只允许特定函数通过fallback调用
    bytes4 funcSelector = _getSelector(msg.data);
    require(_isAllowedFallbackSelector(funcSelector), 
            "TransparentUpgradeableProxy: function not allowed through fallback");

    super._beforeFallback();
}
```

#### 修复二：添加输入验证与安全机制
**修复目标**：防止关键状态被设置任意极端值

**核心补丁代码**：
```solidity
event PriceUpdated(uint256 oldPrice, uint256 newPrice, address indexed updater, uint256 timestamp, string reason);

function setTokenPrice(uint256 newPrice) external returns (uint256) {
    require(msg.sender == admin, "Caller is not admin");

    uint256 oldPrice = getTokenPrice;

    // 1. 添加价格合理性检查（USDT价格应在0.5-2.0范围内，考虑18位小数）
    require(newPrice >= 0.5e18 && newPrice <= 2.0e18, "Price out of valid range (0.5-2.0)");

    // 2. 添加价格变化率限制（单次调整不超过±10%）
    if (oldPrice > 0) {
        uint256 maxChange = oldPrice * 10 / 100;
        require(
            (newPrice <= oldPrice + maxChange && newPrice >= oldPrice - maxChange),
            "Price change exceeds allowed 10% limit"
        );
    }

    // 3. 添加时间锁（24小时冷却期）
    require(block.timestamp >= lastPriceUpdate + 24 hours, "Time lock active: can only update once per 24 hours");

    // 4. 记录详细事件日志
    emit PriceUpdated(oldPrice, newPrice, msg.sender, block.timestamp, "Admin price update");

    // 5. 更新状态
    getTokenPrice = newPrice;
    lastPriceUpdate = block.timestamp;

    return newPrice;
}
```

#### 修复三：修正异常初始状态
**修复目标**：设置合理的初始价格值

**核心补丁代码**：
