## 4. 修复与验证 (Mitigation & Verification)

### 4.1 核心修复策略

#### 修复一：SFM.burn() 函数添加访问控制
**推荐方案 (修复建议2)：保留 from 参数但添加授权检查**
```solidity
function burn(address from, uint256 amount) public {
    // 添加访问控制检查
    if (from != msg.sender) {
        uint256 currentAllowance = allowance(from, msg.sender);
        require(currentAllowance >= amount, "ERC20: burn amount exceeds allowance");
        _approve(from, msg.sender, currentAllowance - amount);
    } else {
        require(balanceOf(from) >= amount, "ERC20: burn amount exceeds balance");
    }
    _tokenTransfer(from, bridgeBurnAddress, amount, ...);
}
```

#### 修复二：sync() 函数添加安全边界
**推荐方案 (修复建议1)：添加工厂合约权限控制**
```solidity
modifier onlyFactory() {
    require(msg.sender == factory, "Only factory can call sync");
    _;
}

function sync() external onlyFactory {
    _update(balance0, balance1, _reserve0, _reserve1);
}
```

**替代方案 (修复建议2)：添加合理性检查**
```solidity
function sync() external {
    // 检查储备与余额的差异是否在合理范围内
    uint256 diff0 = balance0 > _reserve0 ? balance0 - _reserve0 : _reserve0 - balance0;
    uint256 diff1 = balance1 > _reserve1 ? balance1 - _reserve1 : _reserve1 - balance1;
    uint256 maxDiff = (_reserve0 + _reserve1) / 1000; // 允许0.1%的差异
    require(diff0 <= maxDiff && diff1 <= maxDiff, "Sync: abnormal balance change");

    _update(balance0, balance1, _reserve0, _reserve1);
}
```

